# warnings

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] plugins/babel.mjs is dynamically imported by tt.mjs but also statically imported by tt.mjs, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] plugins/postcss.mjs is dynamically imported by tt.mjs but also statically imported by tt.mjs, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

